trans-unit.source: Generates classes for Web services that use the SOAP protocol.
trans-unit.target: Genererer klasser for Web-tjenester som bruker SOAP-protokollen.

trans-unit.source: The SoapProtocolImporter class generates client proxy code or abstract server code according to the SOAP protocol.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SoapProtocolImporter genererer klienten proxy eller abstrakt server kode i henhold til SOAP-protokollen.

trans-unit.source: The class generates a class for each supported binding defined in a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document.
trans-unit.target: Klassen genererer en klasse for hver støttede binding som er definert i et dokument Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL).

trans-unit.source: Typically, instead of invoking SoapProtocolImporter directly, a developer uses the class indirectly through the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> class.
trans-unit.target: I stedet for å aktivere SoapProtocolImporter direkte, bruker vanligvis utvikler klassen indirekte via <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>klasse.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the generation of a binding class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer generering av en klasse med bindingen.

trans-unit.source: During generation of a class for a given binding, the BeginClass method executes before the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class generates methods that correspond to operations.
trans-unit.target: Under generering av en klasse for en gitt binding metoden BeginClass utfører før den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klassen genererer metoder som tilsvarer operasjoner.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: A binding class.
trans-unit.target: En binding klasse.

trans-unit.source: Performs initialization for an entire code namespace during code generation.
trans-unit.target: Utfører initialisering for et navneområde for hele koden under kodegenerering.

trans-unit.source: During code generation, the BeginNamespace method executes before the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class generates classes that represent bindings.
trans-unit.target: Under kodegenerering, utfører metoden BeginNamespace før den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klassen genererer klasser som representerer bindinger.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: Processes a binding class after the generation of methods.
trans-unit.target: Behandler en binding klasse etter generering av metoder.

trans-unit.source: During generation of a class for a given binding, the EndClass method executes after the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class generates methods that correspond to operations.
trans-unit.target: Under generering av en klasse for en gitt binding metoden EndClass utfører etter den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klassen genererer metoder som tilsvarer operasjoner.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: Performs processing for an entire code namespace after binding class generation.
trans-unit.target: Utfører behandling for et navneområde for hele koden etter binding generering av klassen.

trans-unit.source: During code generation, the EndNamespace method executes after the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class generates classes that represent bindings.
trans-unit.target: Under kodegenerering, utfører metoden EndNamespace etter den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klassen genererer klasser som representerer bindinger.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: Generates method code for a binding class.
trans-unit.target: Genererer kode for en binding klasse.

trans-unit.source: During generation of a class for a given binding, the GenerateMethod method executes for each binding class method that represents an operation.
trans-unit.target: Under generering av en klasse for en gitt binding utfører metoden GenerateMethod for hver binding klassemetode som representerer en operasjon.

trans-unit.source: The method code for a binding class.
trans-unit.target: Metoden-koden for en binding klasse.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether a class can be generated for the current binding.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om en klasse kan genereres for gjeldende bindingen.

trans-unit.source: The IsBindingSupported method determines whether to generate a class for the current binding, as represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IsBindingSupported bestemmer om du vil generere en klasse for den gjeldende bindingen, slik det representeres med den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The method checks whether the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A> property's <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding.Extensions%2A> property contains a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding> instance.
trans-unit.target: Metoden kontrollerer om den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A>egenskapens <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding.Extensions%2A>egenskapen inneholder en <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding>forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding.Extensions%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: In addition, the transport mechanism obtained through the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding.Transport%2A> property must be supported by the current Web services configuration.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg transportmekanisme anskaffet via den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding.Transport%2A>egenskapen må støttes av gjeldende konfigurasjon av Web services.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBinding.Transport%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the class can be generated for the current binding; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis klassen kan genereres for gjeldende bindingen; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current operation's operation flow is supported.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om den gjeldende operasjonen operasjonen flyten støttes.

trans-unit.source: The IsOperationFlowSupported method determines whether to generate a method for the current operation, as represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IsOperationFlowSupported bestemmer om du vil generere en metode for den gjeldende operasjonen, slik det representeres med den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation>

trans-unit.source: This evaluation takes place for each operation in a binding for which a class is being generated.
trans-unit.target: Denne evalueringen foregår for hver operasjon i en binding som en klasse genereres.

trans-unit.source: If a `false` value is returned, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.UnsupportedOperationWarning%2A> method executes.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en `false` verdien som returneres av <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.UnsupportedOperationWarning%2A>metoden utfører.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter.UnsupportedOperationWarning%2A>

trans-unit.source: A `true` value is returned only if the input value is <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow>.
trans-unit.target: En `true` , returneres verdien bare hvis inndataverdien <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow>eller <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection.Flow%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection.Flow%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection.Flow%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A> property is of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A>Egenskapen er av typen <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow"></xref> enumeration value that represents a transmission pattern.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow"> </xref> opplistingsverdien som representerer et mønster for overføring.

trans-unit.source: Checks for the presence of "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/" in a string that represents a list of Uniform Resource Indicators (URIs).
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerer om forekomsten av "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/" i en streng som representerer en liste over Uniform Resource indikatorer (URIer).

trans-unit.source: A space-delimited list of URIs.
trans-unit.target: Mellomrom liste over URIer.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object of type <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter"></xref> used internally by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter"></xref> class to generate code from mappings between SOAP-encoded XML schema content and .NET Framework types.
trans-unit.target: Henter objekt av typen <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter"> </xref> brukt internt av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter"> </xref> klassen for å generere kode fra tilordninger mellom SOAP-kodet XML-skjema innhold og .NET Framework-typer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter> class uses a <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter> object to create code from .NET Framework type mappings for XML schema elements and data types that enable SOAP encoding, as opposed to literal XML Schema usage.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>klasse bruker en <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter>objektet for å opprette kode fra .NET Framework typen tilordninger for XML-skjema elementer og datatyper som gjør SOAP-koding i stedet for Litteralen Bruk for XML-skjema.</xref:System.Xml.Serialization.SoapCodeExporter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapProtocolImporter>

trans-unit.source: SOAP encoding is specified in section 5 of the SOAP 1.1 specification.
trans-unit.target: SOAP-koding er angitt under 5 av SOAP 1.1-spesifikasjonen.

trans-unit.source: SOAP encoding uses the namespace "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/".
trans-unit.target: SOAP-koding bruker navneområdet "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/".
